General.Name: Murray Cod Australia Ltd
General.Description: Murray Cod Australia Limited, together with its subsidiaries, engages in breeding, growing, and marketing freshwater table fish in Australia. The company is also involved in breeding and selling Murray Cod, Golden Perch, and Silver Perch as fingerlings. In addition, it constructs and sells aquaculture equipment. The company was incorporated in 2001 and is headquartered in Griffith, Australia.
